MCQ,Choices,Correct
What is biology?,a: The study of rocks | b: The study of life | c: The study of stars | d: The study of computers,b
Which theme in biology explains the unity and diversity of life?,a: Evolution | b: Chemistry | c: Physics | d: Mathematics,a
What is the importance of energy processing in living organisms?,"a: It allows organisms to communicate | b: It allows organisms to move, grow, and reproduce | c: It allows organisms to fly | d: It allows organisms to hibernate",b
Which level of organization in biology involves the study of anatomy and physiology of plants and animals?,a: Molecular biology | b: Cell biology | c: Ecology | d: Organismal biology,d
When did life on Earth emerge?,a: 1 million years ago | b: 500 million years ago | c: 3.7 billion years ago | d: 10 billion years ago,c
